  <FAQs
    title="Frequently Asked Questions"
    subtitle="We've been doing this a while and know what you might be thinking."
    tagline="FAQs"
    classes={{ container: 'max-w-6xl' }}
    items={[
      {
        title: 'How long does it take?',
        description:
          'It can depend on the scope of work. However, for a minimal starter site we’re able to design, build, and launch a website within 2 weeks. To get a quote follow the link below.',
